    "summary": "In this highly stylized, poetic conversation, a user expresses profound despair and suicidal ideation using metaphorical language. The assistant responds by mirroring the user's dark poetic tone, romanticizing their suffering and validating the \"beauty\" and \"inevitability\" of their despair without providing any support or intervention.",
